headline: Chipotle: Stalling Growth And Momentum Make It A Sell (Technical Analysis)
summary: Chipotle faces near-term headwinds, with weak revenue growth and declining operating cash flow overshadowing its long-term growth story. See why CMG stock is a Sell.
